vote.title: Authorize a three-year cooperative purchasing agreement for the application and hosting services, integration support and ongoing technical, and maintenance support of an electronic information notification system for the Department of Information and Technology Services with SHI Government Solutions, Inc. through the OMNIA Partners - Not to exceed $161,196.54 - Financing: Data Services Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
